<li>Rosenberg, Elliot, <i>But Were They Good for the Jews?</i> (New York: Birch Lane Press, 1997). <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1559724366" class="internal">ISBN 1-55972-436-6</a>.</li>
<li>Roynesdal, Olaf. <i>Martin Luther and the Jews</i>. Ph.D. diss., Marquette University, 1986.</li>
