<li><a href="/wiki/Uwe_Siemon-Netto" title="Uwe Siemon-Netto">Siemon-Netto, Uwe</a>. <i>The Fabricated Luther: the Rise and Fall of the Shirer Myth</i>. Peter L. Berger, Foreword. St. Louis: Concordia Publishing House, 1995. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0570048001" class="internal">ISBN 0-570-04800-1</a>.</li>
